  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div xml:id="KT0-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">pāratam pāṭiya peruntēvaṉār
            kaṭavuḷ vāḻttu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Invocatory stanza to Murukaṉ</p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="KT0">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>tāmarai puraiyuṅ kāmar cēvaṭip</l>
<l>pavaḷat taṉṉa mēṉit tikaḻoḷik</l>
<l>kuṉṟi yēykku muṭukkaik kuṉṟi</l>
<l>ṉeñcupaka veṟinta vañcuṭar neṭuvēṟ</l>
<l>cēvalaṅ koṭiyōṉ kāppa</l>
<l>vēma vaika leytiṉṟā lulakē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>           The world verily attained a day of joy,</l>
<l rend="indent">as he with the cock banner protects [it]:</l>
<l>            long spear, hurled with beautiful glow to split
    <choice>
       <seg>hearts,</seg>
       <seg>the heart</seg>
    </choice>
</l>
<l rend="indent">
  <choice>
    <seg>on the hill,</seg>
    <seg>of the mountain,</seg>
  </choice>
</l>
<l rend="indent4">the garment [red] as Kuṉṟi seed,</l>
<l>            glittering brightness the body like coral,</l>
<l>            red feet pretty like lotuses.            </l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>

